183
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:47,795
Hazumi?

184
00:13:47,795 --> 00:13:50,077
Is that the one who was with you the other day?

185
00:13:50,077 --> 00:13:51,245
Yes.

186
00:13:51,245 --> 00:13:53,655
