Ten, hundred, wait, what! No!

192
00:14:10,990 --> 00:14:13,360
Oh, no! So many zeros!

193
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:15,425
Wait... Oh, no!

194
00:14:15,425 --> 00:14:17,600
