236
00:17:11,890 --> 00:17:13,830
That money...

237
00:17:13,830 --> 00:17:17,230
Didn't it come from selling yourself?

238
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:22,680
Oh, I'm sorry.

239
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:25,675
That was rude. I never meant to hurt you.

240
00:17:25,675 --> 00:17:30,095
No, I am sorry for worrying you.

241
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:34,860
But I want to work hard.

242
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:39,570
I'm thinking I'll start with finding a place to live alone, and be independent.

243
00:17:39,570 --> 00:17:40,910
Independent?

244
00:17:40,910 --> 00:17:42,400
Yes.

245
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:46,690
I've been trapped for the past ten years.

246
00:17:46,690 --> 00:17:51,430
I want to find my own happiness.

247
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:58,700
Okay. I will introduce you to a good art vendor.

248
00:17:58,700 --> 00:18:03,290
Rio, you can make a living for yourself by selling your paintings.

249
00:18:03,290 --> 00:18:08,615
No. I cannot cause you any more trouble, Sensei.

250
00:18:08,615 --> 00:18:12,240
I just came by to say hello.

251
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:14,710
Hope to see you again.

252
00:18:14,710 --> 00:18:16,748
